query:
UPDATE task_relationship_types
               SET type_name = $2, 
                   display_name = $3, 
                   description = $4,
                   is_directional = $5,
                   forward_label = $6,
                   reverse_label = $7,
                   enforces_blocking = $8,
                   blocking_disabled_statuses = $9,
                   blocking_source_statuses = $10,
                   updated_at = datetime('now', 'subsec')
               WHERE id = $1
               RETURNING 
                   id as "id!: Uuid", 
                   type_name, 
                   display_name, 
                   description,
                   is_system as "is_system!: bool",
                   is_directional as "is_directional!: bool",
                   forward_label,
                   reverse_label,
                   enforces_blocking as "enforces_blocking!: bool",
                   blocking_disabled_statuses,
                   blocking_source_statuses,
                   created_at as "created_at!: DateTime<Utc>", 
                   updated_at as "updated_at!: DateTime<Utc>"
